CONTEXT ComplementNonEndoCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT ComplementNonEndoCheck
{+ Test that complement succeeds on non-endomorphic relations.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts -t[A*C] even when source and target differ.
+}

RELATION t[A*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testComplementNonEndo: result = -t

ENDCONTEXT
